Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加宽广的领域\N往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒吧，绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快觉醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rah…Xephon…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的MU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点方向出现不明飞行物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是D-1，什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiranipa已经回到了原始坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.09,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hiranipa：MU的浮游都市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin已被回收，送到了最近的医疗设施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…虽然发生了一些意外，但仍在计划之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印成照片，分发下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从olin的书包里发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与从入侵的VTOL采集出来的指纹进行比较
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:10.18,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}VTOL(Vertical Take Off And Landing)：垂直起降飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是约克纳帕塔法2号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.77,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}约克纳帕塔法：在美国作家威兼·福克纳的作品中多次出现的\N虚构的位于密西西比州的一个县的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马贡多4号，请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:19.48,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}马贡多：哥伦比亚魔幻现实主义作家加西亚·马尔克斯\N的名著《百年孤独》中的故事就发生在这个小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是马贡多4号，over
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经确认指纹相同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵的机体回收完成后，就把它运到胡霞市来，over
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.57,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}胡霞市：地名，位于崎玉县南部与东京都的练马区接壤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个，发现我的时候有一个\N女孩子和我在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心，他会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是神名君吧？你的身体好像没有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母亲就要来接你了，换好衣服等她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对昨天旱上8点45分开始的侵略者的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我防卫军进行了勇敢果断的还击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保卫了首都的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在防卫军的新式武器面前，敌军…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重播一遍，针对昨天旱上8点45分\N开始的侵略者的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我防卫军进行了勇敢果断……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天新式武器的战斗你看到没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了，不过距离比较远
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和新式武器战斗的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形状看起来是不是像人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上长着翅膀，非常高大的巨人,\N你看到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到那种东西，当时我不在场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视里也没报道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊，那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有，你离开研究所不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我可爱的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会这样想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了吧，今天好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是美屿宅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我是神名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天为什么突然不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你受了伤，非常担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是神名君你之后没出什么事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细的情况说来话长，明天到学校说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您现在拨打的电话无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请检查电话号码后重拨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we dream？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But recearch by scientists\Nis providing some important clues
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Researchers at the University of Chicago
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example,have been studing a kind of…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你跟我走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于蓝色的血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及这个世界的一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名！神名绫人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名，到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…刚才我走神了，没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名同学常常说\N学习已经消失的国家的语言是在浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是英国和美国已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是英文小说和歌曲还存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去卡拉OK的时候不也会唱beatles的歌曲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然缝了3针，不过听说不会留下伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙脸都绿了，抖得不成样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的皮肤和男人的可大不一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说，没有出大事，太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来，我们分开后你去干什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，我向秋叶原方向跑，路上遇到了美屿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿 玲香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电话里听起来她好像没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎，神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚你在讲什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了玲香？你会迟到可真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿，不会是每个月的那个时候…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？很可疑的气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！你在乱想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此地无银3OO两啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我不认为那是个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君说看到了，那么那个巨人肯定是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:12:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是反映真实的镜子，调奏世界旋律的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的，如果你愿意，你一定能再见到它的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧，绫人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道世界的真实模样吗？\N今晚两点到石神井公国见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复的状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在自我修复中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距完全恢复还有一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“那个家伙”怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还处于休眠状恋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何苏醒的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“让我看看这个世界的真相”是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我见过照片里的东西”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“电视新闻的报道很可疑啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“有人隐瞒了真相吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才回来见我吧，不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者你只是想和昨天遇到的漂亮姐姐见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经说过，我对年长的女性不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道现在地球上有多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的口气就像学校的老师一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快回答问题
