Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？绫人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去
